In this update we focused on small design changes, stability and performance. Any feedback? Please send a mail to ios@theinnercircle.co - Thank you and enjoy The Inner Circle.

P.S. If app crashes on start, please go to Settings -> The Inner Circle -> Location and enable location permissions. Sorry for inconvenience. Quick fix is on the way.
